history.content:
Posting on behalf of the ASUC and BridgeUSA:
Do you live on the Northside of Campus? (near Soda, Cory Hall etc.) Are you interested in local issues like housing, homelessness, or public safety? Not sure who to vote for on November 3rd? Come meet the candidates running to represent you on City Council! We'll start by asking them a few questions about their backgrounds and policies. Then we'll open the event up to you to raise issues you care about in Berkeley and find out where your candidates stand.
Register for the zoom at https://us02web.zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_p7NcTwNHRO-ILqlgqDUJFw or watch on Facebook at https://www.facebook.com/BridgeUSAatBerkeley
If you'd like to submit questions for the candidates in advance of the event, you can submit them here: https://tinyurl.com/eavptownhall
history.subject: Northside City Council Election Townhall (Tonight at 6:30)
